Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.elementary

Class InsertionSortBasic<S>

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.sort.elementary.InsertionSortBasic<S>
Type Parameters:
S - the type of elements to be sorted
public class InsertionSortBasic<S> extends Object
A generic implementation of the insertion sort algorithm. Allows sorting of arrays using either the natural order of elements (when the elements implement Comparable) or a custom Comparator provided during instantiation.

      Sort the array a starting with index from and end just before index to.
      Parameters:
      a - the array of which we must sort a partition.
      from - the lowest index of the partition to be sorted.
      to - one more than the highest index of the partition to be sorted.
